{"tid":2061550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"李柱銘同中共講數","createTime":"2020-06-12T12:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T13:58:14.000Z","uid":69221,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"afc9126125d50f4d3de5fdcb5666c93953a8af41","tid":2061550,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T12:37:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RRZtgv4OTEQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRRZtgv4OTEQ&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c8ed2ca4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RRZtgv4OTEQ</a>"},{"pid":"117b1ba2e8d7b293e1c9137027f8fe4650a3c24d","tid":2061550,"uid":69221,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"82 年訪京曾提出「港獨」遭拒<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘又說，留意到有人提倡「香港獨立」，「獨立係好羅曼蒂克，但行得通咩？」李柱銘更加透露，他早在 1982 年的「訪京團」已經提出過「港獨」。「當時（港澳辦副主任）李後約咗我哋 7 個法律界人士傾計，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">突然間佢話想傾下香港前途問題，我哋 7 個嚇到面都青</span></span>。佢話你哋唔使驚，領導人係想香港繼續穩定繁榮。」時任大律師公會主席的李表示要「講真話」，「我同佢講，你又要繁榮，又要主權，咁係魚與熊掌，不可兼得」"},{"pid":"22bb4fc38636d7d97d157cbfc6eaa7dd712767ba","tid":2061550,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T12:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bc4533c47131b07f141b306b9d1f7404b9730d","tid":2061550,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aa1794264fab6fe973393b81f3275ccfdd20c1","tid":2061550,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"收皮啦港奸 李柱銘死全家"},{"pid":"0a3fe04427b716092a5b740b2789ad9cc5ea0f3b","tid":2061550,"uid":35886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:27:28.000Z","msg":"落去陪司徒華啦"},{"pid":"a620d18e939b3b7f59b9004925f6d64c41f13eb0","tid":2061550,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"